            <title>Version 1.7.0</title>
            <sparkle:version>22</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.7.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <p><strong>What's new in 1.7.0</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Your voice and everyone else's are now always captured as separate streams in real time — no headphones required</li>
                    <li>Plug in or remove AirPods mid-recording without interrupting the session</li>
                    <li>Link speaker labels to real people; 1:1 meetings auto-assign the other speaker</li>
                    <li>Voice enrollment removed — no longer needed</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
