        <item>
            <title>Version 1.4.0</title>
            <sparkle:version>16</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.4.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <p><strong>Note attributes</strong> — Add and remove people, organizations, and calendar events on any note via the new "+" dropdown. Searchable autocomplete pulls from names already in your notes. Calendar event picker groups by date. Hover any chip to remove it.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Recurring calendar events now correctly create a separate note for each occurrence instead of all mapping to the same one</li>
                    <li>Names with commas (e.g. "John Smith, Jr.") are no longer split into separate entities</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 14:06:12 +0000</pubDate>
