        <item>
            <title>Version 1.2.0</title>
            <sparkle:version>12</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>New</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Per-item summaries</strong> — each agenda item gets its own AI summary after a recording, based on what was actually discussed. See exactly what moved on each topic without reading the full transcript.</li>
                    <li><strong>API key management, redesigned</strong> — connect your own OpenAI, Anthropic, or Google key and choose from any model each provider offers. Keys are stored securely on your Mac.</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>Fixed</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Agenda items no longer disappear after clicking Done or adding a new item</li>
                    <li>The error message when Apple Intelligence models are still downloading is now clearer</li>
                    <li>Notes list sidebar no longer resets when navigating to and from Settings</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>Improved</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>File sync is now activation-based — edits you make in Obsidian, iA Writer, or any other app are picked up the moment you switch back to Thunder Kitty</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 14:03:07 +0000</pubDate>
